        "slug": "welcome-to-emdash",
        "excerpt": "A seeded blog post proving the EmDash import path from source payload to public rendering.",
        "content": "<p>EmDash content now lands in tenant-scoped AWCMS records through a replayable import flow.</p><p>This sample seed verifies blog creation, widget-area preservation, and public single-post rendering from one atomic import step.</p><p>External producers can copy this file and replace titles, slugs, HTML, widget payloads, and visual template content.</p>",
